=== ApplicationNumber ===

we agreed to use 0xA000 to 0xAFFF:

* 0xA000 to 0xA0FF (40960 to 41215): reserved for mumpf
* 0xA100 to 0xA1FF (41216 to 41471): reserved for SirSydom
* 0xA200 to 0xA2FF (41472 to 41727): reserved for Masifi
* 0xAF00 to 0xAFFF (44800 to 45055): reserved for Testing/Debugging etc... (no public usage)

Following ApplicationNumbers are already in use:

* 0xA000 (40960) - PresenceModule (mumpf)
* 0xA010 (40976) - SensorModule (mumpf)
* 0xA020 (40992) - OneWireGateway (mumpf)
* 0xA030 (41008) - LogicModule (mumpf)
* 0xA040 (41024) - SensorVpmModule (mumpf)
* 0xA200 (41472) - EnocenGateway (masifi)
* 0xA210 (41488) - GardenControl (masifi)
* 0xA220 (41504) - 28CH Binäreingang (masifi)
* 0xA230 (41520) - ModbusGateway (masifi)

